It is considered a possible location (論社) for {{ill|Takada Shrine (Hida Province)|ja|高田神社|12=draft}}, an {{ill|Enshrinement in the Engishiki|ja|延喜式神名帳|12=draft}}-listed shrine of {{ill|Araki District, Hida Province|ja|荒城郡|12=draft}}, Hida Province. Another contender for this title is {{ill|Takada Shrine (Hida)|ja|高田神社 (飛騨市)|12=draft}}.
